title: The Diet
description: Gumball and Darwin discover the reason Dad's diet wasn't working was that he was actually on ten diets and eating a meal for each of them. They eventually manage to help him lose weight, but Richard's newfound buffness also brings out his more obnoxious side.

title: Swing Set Jet Set
description: Axel and the team battle Princess SugarSalt for possession of Bearbarian's hammer, traded to her by one of their own - Galileo!

title: The Past Car
description: Tulip takes a risk trusting an old foe.

title: Thick as Thieves
description: Phil the Pilferer robs Vambre and Prohyas of their very best Magiswords so he can snag the Sheepy Mantis, but the Warriors find out that no Magisword is lame as they manage to keep Phil from becoming Thief of the Year.

title: The Crossroads Part 1
description: An attempt to use a derelict SpaceBridge sends The Ark to Unspace!

title: Time Share
description: Batman and Blue Beetle have to travel back in time to stop Chronos from destroying a young Dark Knight on his very first case.

title: Parley Part 1
description: Megatron and Optimus parley in an attempt to unite against Starscream.

title: Wisdom, Strength, and Charisma
description: When Enid goes to a new school, KO sets out to make sure she fits in.

title: Zombie King
description: Grundy escapes his Louisiana prison intent on using a magical crystal which will allow him to raise the dead from their graves. Only Batman and Swamp thing stand in the way of his growing zombie army.

title: The Library
description: The campers spend a rainy day at the library.

title: Felonious Prose
description: The Warrior mission of finding a lost contact lens gets seriously compromised from Vambre's obsession with the latest Veronica Victorious novel.

title: Special Delivery
description: Enid and Rad go on a road trip to deliver a package.

title: Alone Quest
description: Craig has an "emergency" leaving Kelsey alone at the Stump.

title: Bring Me the Spark of Optimus Prime Part 1
description: The Decepticons compete to be the first to bring Megatron Optimus Prime's spark while Hot Rod chases the "Moon Cheetah."

title: Communicate Openly
description: Bumbleebee becomes the 6th Titan and moves into the Tower but has a hard time adjusting.

title: Game Show
description: While shopping with his Mom, Clarence discovers Breehn hiding in a clothes rack. Under the guise of trying on new clothes for their moms, they sneak out to find a local gameshow being hosted inside the Aberdale Mall.

title: Classic Rock
description: Batman thinks he's helping a homeless old man who is being mugged on the street only to discover that the man is a powerful wizard being chased by demons in disguise. It turns out the wizard is on a mission to save Shazam from the clutches of Black Adam.

title: Block Party
description: Apple and Onion have to outwit a mean duck who's taken over their building's roof.

title: Side Kicked
description: Zoe builds her own battle suit in hopes of joining Axel's team. The only problem? She can't shrink! Hijinks ensue as a full-sized Zoe tries to assist Axel & co. in a battle against Pyrant and his army of mind-control drones.

title: On Nagual Hill
description: Vic & Val take over a forest hill and build an epic waterslide, disturbing the plants and animals that normally inhabit it. But when a Nagual (a human with the power to transform into animals) transforms Vic into a chicken and Val into a donkey, they learn to sympathize with the animals and understand the world a bit more.

title: The Mystery of the Timekeeper
description: When the Time Keeper goes missing, Craig and his friends take up the task of helping kids get home in time for dinner.

title: The Crystal Car
description: Tulip, Atticus, and One-One enter a crystal forest car and have to take part in a musical ritual.

title: Pancake's Bus Tour
description: Apple and Onion go on a guided bus tour as part of their plan to get Apple's shoe back.

title: Comunicacion abierta
description: Bumblebee se convierte en la sexta Titán y se muda a la torre, pero tiene problemas para adaptarse.

title: La Casa del Arbol
description: Vic y Val construyen una casa en el árbol, y Val se libra de Vic con una tarea sin importáncia para construir la casa exactamente como quiere. Pero cuando Vic regresa y trae, sin saberlo, una rama del Árbol Vampiro, la casa del árbol perfecta de Val se convierte en una pesadilla.

title: La princesa de jade
description: A raíz de un cruel ataque al Palacio, Los Hijos de Garmadon roban la segunda Máscara Oni, y los ninjas invitan a la Princesa Real, Harumi, a su improvisada familia.

title: Bobbie Not Blobby
description: Axel discovers that the culprit behind Bobbie Blobby's missing mech-suit is Masko, who only wanted to clean out its clogged clay cannons, but lets the suit fall into the hands (or tentacles) of Dr. Nautilus - intent on flooding the sewers!

title: The Golden Forge/A Deep Hibernation
description: The Golden Forge: As Dan and Drago battle to free Trhyno from Tiko's infection, they learn the history of Vestroia and the nature of Golden Bakugan./A Deep Hibernation: Trhyno must give Dan and Drago the power they need if they are to have any chance in stopping Tiko from destroying both Vestroia and Earth.

title: Sea of Tranquility Part 1
description: Optimus Prime and the Autobots battle Megatron and the Deceptions on Earth's Moon.

title: You Are Rad
description: When KO forgets his name tag, Rad lets him use his, which results in everyone thinking KO is Rad, including Rad himself.

title: Hotdog's Movie Premiere
description: Apple and Onion square off against a no-nonsense security guard after they're banned from the premiere of their friend Hot Dog's new movie.

title: El chillido de hombre muerto
description: La casi desaparición de Zane a manos del Señor "E" obliga a los ninjas a huir a bordo del Bounty, donde descubren que una tramisión que Zane interceptó puede revelar la ubicación oculta del "Silencioso".

title: Lonely Haunts Club 2: Doll Island
description: In order to prove their bravery, V&V head to a haunted island to retrieve a special doll, but Charlene and Pineapple are intent on getting it first.

title: Mystery Sleepover
description: KO, Enid and Rad attempt to solve a mystery.

title: Trials Part 1
description: Following the network of GroundBridges left by the Allspark, Optimus and Megatron finally discover the Allspark, and its Guardian, Cheetor.

title: Party Down Part 2
description: A malfunction in Wheeljack's party favors turns most of the Autobot crew feral, leaving Optimus, Cheetor, and Teletraan-X in a race to save their friends.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Secret of the Wolf
description: The Ice Emperor summons an enormous ice Behemoth to attack Lloyd and his faithful wolf companion.

title: Dungeons and Dayjobs
description: A botched mission leaves the Warriors in debt, so they take day jobs at Slugburger and sling Slugburgers for Witchy Simone!

title: El Silbon
description: Victor sets up a haunted corn maze, but the town kids think it's lame. Vic decides to make the maze scarier by enlisting the help of El Silbon (The Whistler) to really scare the kids, but El Silbon has plans of his own.

title: Uncle Grandpa at the Movies
description: When Uncle Grandpa and Pizza Steve cause a ruckus at the movies, Mr. Gus is forced to play the hero in order to save the day.

title: Twelve Angry Hedgehogs
description: Hedgehog wants to win the Golden Science Badge but runs into some unexpected competition.

title: Fogata de campamento!
description: Los Titanes montan un espectáculo, pero Robin les advierte que la actuación debe ser aburrida o despertarán a los lobos.

title: Dr. Animo and the Mutant Ray
description: Dr. Animo has broken out of jail, and has been tracking down Ben, intent on revenge. At the same time, Ben's broken off a piece of the Omnitrix, and as a result, has turned into weird alien combinations, i.e. StinkArms.

title: Game of Masks
description: As Lloyd and Harumi search the Oni Temple for the last mask, the ninja are taken hostage and discover Princess Harumi's true intentions.

title: Steam Fight at the OK Corral
description: When Kevin convinces Steam Smythe to adopt a modern approach in fighting Ben, our young hero must resort to old-fashioned thinking to save the day.

title: Bedtime Stories
description: When Puppycorn can't fall asleep, Dr. Fox uses an invention to bring classic bedtime stories to life. But the gang's presence leads to some surprising twists in these popular tales.

title: Classroom
description: Over the course of a single day in Ms. Baker's class, we see how Clarence and his classmates deal with their individual trials during the school day.

title: True Potential
description: Just when the Ninja think they have saved the day, Lord Garmadon returns to Ninjago, and frees Harumi, who encourages him to "achieve his true potential" by conquering the one thing that has always stood in his way, his son, Lloyd.

title: Mision solitaria
description: Craig debe atender una "emergencia", dejando a Kelsey sola en el Tronco.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Apoca-lice Now
description: When Chef brokers a truce with lice by selecting three kids to "host" them on their heads, Courtney instigates a kid vs. lice war.

title: Burrito
description: Grizz likes Burritos. A lot. So much so that after a restaurant makes a Bear-Sized Burrito, Grizz can't bring himself to eat such a majestic work of art. He carries the burrito everywhere making it a new and increasingly smelly part of his life.

title: Porcupunk Rock
description: Madcap turns to Axel and his team for help after a sonic upgrade to Porcupunk threatens to bring down the house.

title: Noche de chicas Parte 2
description: Cuando Blackfire pone en marcha su plan para conquistar la Tierra, las chicas deben intentarlo todo para derrotarla.

title: The Gauntlet Part 1
description: Lord Obsidian unites the Robot Masters against Mega Man and his family for an epic showdown at the Lighthouse.

title: I Am the Allspark Part 2
description: Optimus seemingly sacrifices himself to get the Allspark back from Starscream, leaving the rest of the Autobots to deal with Megatron.

title: Bad Bad Cop
description: Vambre and Prohyas pretend to be cops in their attempts to shakedown a dangerous bunch of pirates to find a broccoli smuggler.

title: Weiner Takes All
description: After forgetting to book a Hot Diggity Doggity Dog mascot on National Hotdog Day, Chef tries to pass off an Australian man dressed as a kangaroo as a substitute.

title: Weapon of Choice
description: Worried that his sword is a glorified consolation prize, Mao Mao sets out to prove the worth of his weapon.

title: 4 on 1
description: Onion's fear of crowds threatens his basketball team's success.

title: Our Stuff
description: After the bears play a little pickup basketball (they're very bad), they go back to grab their stuff by the side of the court only to find it's been stolen!  The Bears race across town trying to track down their stuff and end up cracking a giant case in the process.

title: Bobo Chan
description: Badgerclops adopts an abandoned monster, but some things are better left in the wild.

title: Strength of a Grown Man
description: Needing a hero with shrinking powers, but forgetting about Bumblebee, Robin invites The Atom to join their fight against the Brain.

title: Hot Dog estrena su pelicula
description: Cuando unos guardias de seguridad muy serios los echan del estreno de la nueva película de su amigo Hot Dog, Manzana y Cebollín se preparan para pelear.

title: Curses/Bang for Your Buck
description: Curses: When Bubbles overhears the Professor saying some bad words, the girls add a whole new slew of adjectives to their vocabulary./Bang for Your Buck: When the girls and the Gangreen Gang discover a destructo ray for sale at Mojo's Yard Sale, each team sets out to see who can earn the most money and buy it first.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Girls Night In Part 1
description: The Girls Night Out Crew decide to stay in and have a slumber party but an unknown alien threat descends on Jump City.

title: Dead Man's Squall
description: Zane's near demise at the hands of Mr. E forces the ninja to flee aboard the Bounty, where they discover that a transmission Zane intercepted may reveal the hidden location of the Quiet One.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Fan
description: Sarah, the new kid in school, is Gumball and Darwin's number one, slightly obsessive, fan. Sarah is intensely following Gumball and Darwin around trying to win their friendship.  When Gumball tells her that she is acting like a stalker, she embraces it and actually takes it up a notch.  However, when Gumball and Darwin realise that she's behaving this way because she's lonely, they go to surprising lengths to make her feel accepted.

title: Grown Up Stuff
description: Puppycorn doesn't want to grow up. To ease his woes, Unikitty spends the day teaching him all the fun things about being an adult.

title: Dark Birth Part 1
description: While Starscream acquires new power through the Allspark, the Autobots mistakenly assume Starscream is still under Megatron's command.

title: Ghost Town Part 1
description: When Windblade mysteriously steals the Allspark, Optimus, Bumblebee, Hot Rod and Cheetor follow her to a strange abandoned city.

title: Noche de chicas Parte 1
description: El equipo de la Noche de Chicas decide quedarse en casa y celebrar una pijamada, pero una desconocida amenaza alienígena desciende sobre Jump City.

title: El silencioso
description: Mientras que Lloyd y Harumi se aventuran a lo profundo de "Primeval's Eye" en busca de la tercer máscara Oni, los ninja tratan de arreglar al Bounty y hacer un descubrimiento sorprendente.

title: Get Back Jojo
description: Mojo goes back in time to try and stop the Professor from having the inspiration for the perfect little girls. Little does he know that in doing so he provides just the spark the young Professor needs.

title: Small
description: Mao Mao's legendary, gigantic and critical father visits his son at his new job as sheriff.

title: Power Up Puff
description: During a fight, both Buttercup and Bubbles are surprised to discover they've leveled up, leaving Blossom to wonder when or if she'll get new powers too.

title: Access Denied
description: When Axel and the team try to figure out what Sarge Charge's secret weapon is, they get ejected from the house by his newly upgraded security system and must fight their way back inside before Madcap does.

title: Dibs Court
description: When a kid claims dibs on the Stump, Craig has no choice but to take them to court. Dibs Court.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Shirt Club
description: Steven and Buck Dewey make t-shirts together.

title: No Honor Among Bros
description: Rook is under the influence of Fistrick's "bro" essence, and starts to act like a bro. Can he and Ben infiltrate an alien fight club to claim the Golden Fist? (Introducing Slix Vigma, alien promoter.)

title: Secret Science Part 1
description: While studying the scraplets Wheeljack is kidnapped by Shockwave who tries to enlist Wheeljack's help.

title: En la colina Nahual
description: Vic y Val se apoderan de la colina de un bosque y construyen un tobogán de agua épico que perturba a las plantas y animales que solían habitar allí. Pero cuando un nahual (un humano con el poder de transformarse en animales) transforma a Vic en un pollo y a Val en un burro, ambos aprenden a empatizar con los animales y a entender el mundo un poco más.

title: The Grid Car
description: Tulip, a headstrong 13-year-old girl, finds a mysterious train where every car contains its own universe.

title: Meet Tanya Keys
description: When bounty hunter Tanya Keys comes to town for Badgerclops, it's up to Mao Mao and Adorabat to save their friend -- even if he's been on the wrong side of the law.

title: Mystery Girl
description: After Clarence and pals call random numbers as a prank, Clarence ends up connecting with a girl and they strike up a friendship. But will this long distance phone pal last?

title: Gatocalipsis
description: Cuando Vic se enferma y debe reposar en su cuarto, espía a Piña y queda convencido de que está creando un ejército de gatos zombis. Val está de acuerdo con él y ambos se obsesionan con detener a Piña antes de que sea demasiado tarde.

title: Campfire!
description: The Titans put on a show but Robin warns that the performance must be boring or else they'll wake up the wolves.

title: Tree Buds
description: Vic and Val build a treehouse and Val dismisses Vic with a frivolous task so he can build the treehouse exactly how he wants. But when Vic returns unknowingly with a branch from El Arbol Vampiro, Val's perfect treehouse turns into a nightmare!

title: Snake Jaguar
description: In order to join the Sons of Garmadon, Zane (aka Snake Jaguar) participates in a deadly motorcycle initiation race.

title: Perfect Storm Part 2
description: Arcee and Grimlock get an adventure they never bargained for as they protect the helpless Ark from all manner of space anomalies.

title: A Door Closes, A Door Opens/Kazami's Gambit
description: A Door Closes, A Door Opens: Shun must stand up to his father, expose his cousin and protect his friends before Masato destroys everyone on Ichiro's island!/Kazami's Gambit: When Magnus looks to steal the Dimensional Doorway, Shun and Ichiro must make peace while the AO stop the Doorway from destroying them all.

title: Ninjago chico, problemas grandes
description: Los ninjas corres a salvar a Lloyd. Un Lord Garmadon más poderoso que nunca, crea una enorme estatua para ayudarlo a gobernar Ninjago y a derrotar a los ninjas.

title: Follow that Space Cab!
description: While Superman escorts his prisoner Mr. Mind between planets, he is attacked by Lobo who wants to collect a reward on Mind. Temporarily powered-down, Superman seeks Space Cabbie's help to get away from Lobo.

title: Guar serpiente
description: Para unirse a Los Hijos de Garmadon, Zane (alias Jaguar Serpiente) participa en una carrera de iniciación mortal de motocicletas.

title: Night of the Bat
description: Superman and other Justice League members have to battle Batman when he gets possessed by an evil Djinn, Uthool, who is intent on using the JL power core to blow a crack in Earth.

title: #MeetTheCheetah
description: Barbara Minerva is super-jealous of  "little Miss Perfect" Diana Prince. But when she uses an ancient artifact from her dad's collection to place a curse on Diana, it turns out that Diana's not the one who's cursed. It's Barbara.

title: Juego de mascaras
description: Mientras Lloyd y Harumi buscan el templo Oni para la última máscara, los ninjas son tomados como rehenes y descubren que verdaderas intensiones de la Princesa Harumi.

title: Bad Moon Rising Part 2
description: The Autobots work to stop the Moon from crashing into the Earth as Starscream must reckon with betraying Megatron.

title: Viral Video
description: The Bears think they have what it takes to make and star in a viral video, but when Nom-Nom decides that they don't, Grizz breaks into the koala's limo in an effort to change his mind.

title: Perfect Storm Part 1
description: Arcee and Grimlock go off on an adventure only to return and discover the Ark without power and their friends all in stand-by mode.

title: Same Old World
description: Steven flies around the world.

title: The Traveler's Tree
description: Guilt-ridden over having lost the Traveler's Tea, Cole embarks on a dangerous quest to the top of a nearby mountain in hopes of finding the legendary Traveler's Tree - a tree which is supposedly guarded by a fearsome beast.

title: Krag's Lament
description: Cole awakens inside an icy cavern belonging to a legendary beast, and attempts to escape, only to discover a surprising truth.

title: Awesome vs. AAAnimus
description: Awesome V Aaanimus, Part 1: The AO plan on sneaking into AAAnimus and rescuing their Bakugan but are stopped by Benton who offers up an alternate plan./Awesome V Aaanimus, Part 2: The AO team up with Benton Dusk to recapture their stolen Bakugan and free the energy from the Mind Core Cell under the control of AAAnimus.

title: What Rhymes with Omnitrix?
description: At a poetry slam event, Charmcaster's reading of Kevin's poetry causes magical trouble for Ben and Gwen, causing mind swaps that have everyone confused as to who's fighting who.

title: Trials Part 2
description: Cheetor attempts to judge whether Optimus or Megatron are more worthy of the Allspark, but an unexpected visitor dashes all the bots' plans.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Infinite Vendetta Part 1
description: The Autobots and Decepticons are surprised by the return of their long-lost comrades, Jetfire and Skybyte.

title: The Engine
description: Tulip makes it to the front of the train and is faced with a choice.

title: Fallen Arches/The Mane Event
description: Fallen Arches: When a gang of old-time villains come out of retirement, the girls enlist the best superhero team of the past to save the city./The Mane Event: Bubbles and Buttercup are playing with Blossom's beautiful locks when an accident happens. Now, Blossom is too embarrassed to put up a good fight.

title: Meet Lion-O
description: Meet Lion-O and the Thundercats! After fleeing their home planet, the Thundercats find themselves stranded on Third Earth where they face the evil Mumm-Ra. But Lion-O is strong! He's tough! There's nothing he can't do! Except maybe open really big jars of cookies…

title: The Visitor Part 1
description: Bumblebee searches for any information his fellow Autobots might have regarding a strange creature he saw on the Moon.

title: Starscream's Children Part 2
description: Starscream reveals his scraplet army, incapacitating the Autobots and Decepticons and setting up a show down between him and Cheetor.

title: La Gran Fiebre de Fosiles
description: JP encuentra un fósil en el Arroyo, lo que causa que el paisaje cambie rápidamente.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Iced Out
description: Madcap's latest creation, the Ice Crusher, puts the whole city in a deep freeze, forcing Axel and the team to face him in a game of high-stakes hockey or risk slip-sliding into another ice age!

title: The Corgi Car
description: Tulip and One-One explore a car full of Corgis and face off against a mysterious monster.

title: Escape From Earth Part 2
description: With the Ark extricated from Mt. St. Hilary, the Autobots must run the gauntlet of Decepticon forces to escape Earth with the Allspark.

title: And Then There Were None
description: Vilgax and Eon team up to wipe out every Ben in every dimension!

title: Sea of Tranquility Part 2
description: The Autobots struggle to stop the Decepticon's planet-cracking weapon as it targets Earth.

title: Attack of Thermometron 9000
description: Axel must wrangle Galileo and Bobbie to shut down a rogue thermostat - improperly upgraded by Slobot - as it plunges the house into extreme hot and cold zones.

title: #SuperWho?
description: Overwhelmed by the amount of Superman coverage in Metropolis, Supergirl decides to get out there and really show the city what she can do. But when Superman inadvertently puts everyone in harm's way, Supergirl has to decide whether to do what's good for the people or what's good for her ego.

title: Painbow
description: When a mysterious rainbow causes everyone to become unnaturally happy, the Powerpuff Girls must find where it ends to save the day and return Townsville to normal.

title: Jean Jacket
description: The Bears find a bedazzled jean jacket in a dumpster. It's just about the coolest thing they've ever seen and seems to make the wearer of the jacket extremely lucky. But after the Bears fight over who gets control of the jacket, they have to consider that their denim blessing has become a curse.

title: Uncle Baseball
description: A failing little league team on the brink of giving up gets help from Uncle Grandpa and some Major League Baseball players.

title: Steven Floats
description: Steven is so excited to be back home that he jumps for joy and jumps way too high.

title: Parley Part 2
description: The Autobot-Decepticon peace talks breaks down after Slipstream returns with a dire warning.

title: Don't Look
description: At the top of Dead Mountain, Finn discovers a treasure that comes with a terrible price.

title: Uncle Dummy
description: Uncle Grandpa and Pizza Steve try to convince Mr. Gus that his ventriloquist dummy is alive.

title: Escape from the Citadel
description: Finn and Jake follow the Lich of the Citadel, where Finn meets his long lost dad. But just how far does the apple fall from the tree?

title: La fuerza de un hombre adulto
description: Necesitando un héroe con poderes para encogerse, Robin se olvida de Bumblebee e invita a Átomo a unirse a su pelea contra El Cerebro.

title: El verdadero potencial
description: Justo cuando los ninjas piensan que han salvado el día, Lord Garmadon regresa a Ninjago, y libera a Harumi, quien lo anima a "alcanzar su verdadero potencial" conquistando lo único que siempre se interpuso en su camino, su hijo, Lloyd.

title: Bring Me the Spark of Optimus Prime Part 2
description: Slipstream searches for her missing Seekers while Hot Rod's "Moon Cheetah" chase brings him unexpectedly aboard the Nemesis.

title: The Console
description: When Gumball is given a cursed videogame console, Elmore becomes trapped inside a fantasy RPG world. Gumball, Darwin and Anais have to battle their way through town, unraveling the secrets of their new virtual reality. But they'll have to level up if they're going to stand any chance against the mysterious final boss.

title: Champions of Breakfast
description: An epic battle between Vambre and her Waffle Magisword and Prohyas' Pancake Magisword escalates to a war that can only end when Grup solicits his Cave Weirdo pals to be peacemakers.

title: The Visitor Part 2
description: Dino-Mode Grimlock careens out-of-control around the Ark after drinking Wheeljack's hyper-fuel.

title: Dream Scheme/You Snooze, You Lose
description: Dream Scheme: The Sandman would like a little rest so he puts the world to sleep. The girls must battle him in his dreams to get things back to normal./You Snooze, You Lose: When the Amoeba Boys find Mojo's plan to destroy the Powerpuff Girls, the girls unwittingly help them build a machine for their own destruction.

title: La mascara del engano
description: Cuando un sindicato de criminals desconocido amenaza a la Familia Real, los ninjas son llamados de nuevo a la acción y deben proteger a la princesa real y un artefacto legendario que puede tener poderes sobrenaturales.

title: Questing For Quests
description: Realizing they have gone soft, the ninja search for a quest to reignite their Spinjitzu training. Unfortunately, NINJAGO City is enjoying a period of rare tranquility.

title: El Atajo
description: Un día inusualmente caluroso en el Arroyo derrite todos los helados de Kit, así que Craig la ayuda a encontrar un atajo para llegar a su proveedor de bocadillos helados antes de que todos los demás se derritan.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Girls Night In Part 2
description: When Blackfire begins her plan to conquer Earth, the girls must pull out all the stops to defeat her.

title: I Don't Like You
description: Ben and Gwen's social media battle with Kevin 11 quickly escalates into an all-out war in real life.

title: Legend of Torbaclaun
description: When the Sweetypies think the mythical Torbaclaun has come to Pure Heart Valley, Mao Mao tries to prove to them that it isn't real.

title: 4 a 1
description: El temor de Cebollín a las multitudes amenaza el éxito de su equipo de baloncesto.

title: Weapon XI Part 1
description: Kevin and Argit attempt to warn the amalgam kids about the Rooters intentions meanwhile Ben, Rook, and Gwen set off to find Kevin and land themselves in the Null Void!

title: The Message
description: Lloyd and his wolf-companion find a cave with the mech inside and a message from Zane that provides a clue to his fate.

title: The Jade Princess
description: In the wake of a vicious attack upon the palace, the Sons of Garmadon steal the second Oni Mask, and the ninja invite the royal princess, Harumi, into their makeshift family.

title: Ello Gov'nor
description: After watching a scary movie about a British Taxi, the guys have to help Rigby overcome his fears.

title: Party Down Part 1
description: On their way to back to Cybertron, the Autobots attempt to have some well-deserved fun by throwing a party.

title: The Dynamo Dynamic
description: Axel finds himself at the center of a disagreement between Sarge and Masko over what's more important in battle - the weapon or the one who wields it - after Dynamo bonds the trio together!

title: The Quiet One
description: As Lloyd and Harumi venture deep into Primeval's Eye in search of the third Oni Mask, the ninja attempt to fix the Bounty and make a startling discovery.

title: Bad Moon Rising Part 1
description: Starscream makes a play for leadership of the Deceptions as the Autobots storm the Decepticon's Moon Base.

title: Are You Ready for Some Megafootball?!
description: Lakewood's Megafootball team takes on their rival in a big game.

title: Seek and Hide/Family First
description: Seek and Hide: Sent to investigate a Japanese island by Benton Dusk, the AO discover a hidden facility conducting experiments that affect The Hide./Family First: Trapped by his father, Shun is forced to battle his own friends, revealing dark secrets about the Kazami family and Masato's experiments.

title: You Remind Me of Someone
description: Ben and Gwen look for the infamous Bojamboo (the Bigfoot of the South) and discover that it's actually the Forgeti, at the same time as Kevin 11, but when Ben and Kevin are blasted with the Forgeti's forgetfulness mist, they reverse roles and it's up to Gwen and Max to restore them back to normal.

title: Exodus Part 1
description: Fleeing the destruction of their home planet Thundera, Lion-O and the ThunderCats land on the mysterious, dangerous, all-around awesome world of Third Earth! But their enemies, the Mutants of Plun-Darr have followed them and it turns out Third Earth already has a Mumm-Ra problem, can Lion-O learn the ropes of being a leader in time?

title: Atrapa la Botella
description: Manzana y Cebollín inventan un nuevo juego que atrae una atención inesperada.

title: Film Flam
description: A sleazy director arrives in Townsville to make a film about the Powerpuff Girls. But this Hollywood type wants more out of Townsville than an Oscar-winning film.

title: Elemental
description: Ice King discovers something buried deep beneath the Ice Kingdom that could change Ooo forever.

title: Fiesta en la Cuadra
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben ser más astutos que un pato malvado que se apoderó del techo de su edificio.

title: #HateTriangle
description: When Hal's ex-girlfriend shows up at the Metropolis High homecoming game and goes love-ballistic as the villain Star Sapphire, Jessica begins to second-guess her own nonviolent tactics.

title: Baila Reynaldo Baila
description: Vic está desesperado por ganar el premio en efectivo para el concurso de baile en Monte Macabro y está frustrado porque Val, su pareja, no le deja tomar todas las decisiones. Por eso, elige un compañero diferente: Reynaldo. Pero Vic presiona demasiado a Reynaldo para hacer realidad su visión artística. Al final, Vic aprende que, para tener éxito, hay que ser socios en igualdad de condiciones.

title: Unboxing Part 1
description: Axel ventures into his uncle's strictly off-limits basement lab in hopes of fixing a broken toy and ends up unleashing living ones instead: the renegade Madcap and a whole team of superpowered toys dedicated to stopping him!

title: Sausage and Sweetie Smash
description: Apple and Onion must conquer their obsessions of sausages and a video game.

title: Make the Cut
description: Mega Man goes on a 24/7 heroing spree around the city, forcing Suna, Bert, Ashley, and Rush to deal with the problem at hand, Cut Man.

title: Fancy Restaurant
description: Muscle Man has to impress his girlfriend's parents at a fancy dinner.

title: All Trick No Treat
description: On Halloween, Axel gets too caught up in the scares and loses track of the fun - just in time for an infiltration by the worst trick 'r' treater of all, Madcap!

title: Driving Miss Crazy
description: Duncan leads Beth to believe she's broken his battery-powered bike and makes her chauffeur him around in a wagon for the day as punishment.

title: Spotted Part 1
description: Worried about finding a useful position among the Autobots, Cheetor learns how to become an Autobot Scout from Bumblebee.

title: Escape From Earth Part 1
description: Optimus struggles to recover from using the Matrix of Leadership while the Autobots attempt to get the Allspark back to Cybertron.

title: Wiped Out Part 2
description: Separated from his friends, Cheetor is captured by the territorial Sharkticons who enlist him in their fight over the last remaining bits of their destroyed planet.

title: Tiara Trouble
description: Bubbles' excitement over being a contestant in the Townsville Beauty, Talent and All-Around Flair pageant is ruined when Blossom and Buttercup become overbearing stage-sisters. But when a mysterious tiara causes trouble for the contestants, they realize there are bigger problems at hand.

title: The Rooters of All Evil
description: Meet the Rooters, the Black Ops wing of the Plumbers from the Null Void. They've come looking for someone close to Ben, and they mean business!

title: Clarence Wendle and the Eye of Coogan
description: Clarence and other students find the crusty old journal of Coogan filled with clues leading to a mysterious treasure. Clarence spearheads the team of treasure hunters to journey through the perils of Aberdale seeking the lost Eye of Coogan.

title: The Vengers
description: Billy Billions, Kangaroo Kommando, and Captain Nemesis team up to take down Ben, and claim his place as protector of Bellwood?!?

title: Bottle Catch
description: Apple and Onion's favorite game attracts some unexpected attention.

title: Gnome More Mister Nice Guy
description: When the daycare gets taken over by evil gnomes, Duncan finds himself on the wrong team.

title: #Beeline
description: When she stumbles across a villainous plot to blow up a bridge, Bumblebee shies from the challenge of taking on the baddies and reaches out to her friends. But when the other heroes are all indisposed, it'll take every ounce of courage Bumblebee has to rise to the occasion … despite being the smallest of the bunch.

title: El Misterio de la Guardiana del Tiempo
description: Cuando la Guardiana del Tiempo desaparece, Craig y sus amigos asumen la tarea de ayudar a otros niños a llegar a casa a tiempo para la cena.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: The Tails of Mardrynia
description: After reading a book about a mystical animal society in class, Clarence is inspired to round up local animals and recreate an animal world of his own to cheer up his friend Percy. But will Percy take the game too far?

title: At the Beginning, an Ending/This Late Hour
description: At the Beginning, an Ending: When Shun and Lia track down Ichiro and Masato on their quest for more allies, they are forced to battle a Bakuzoned Ichiro!/This Late Hour: Shun, Lia and Masato must square off against the Dusk Forces, but they are not alone when they are joined by Lt. Brenan and Kino.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Unboxing Part 2
description: Axel discovers that he can transform into a toy and teams up with his new team of toys to stop Madcap from stealing a Minergy battery.

title: El Silbon
description: Víctor arma un laberinto de maíz embrujado, pero los chicos del pueblo creen que es muy malo. Vic decide hacer que el laberinto sea más aterrador con la ayuda de El Silbón para asustar de verdad a los chicos, pero El Silbón tiene sus propios planes.

title: A Change of Face
description: In Salem Massachusetts, Ben, Gwen and Max once again go up against Charmcaster, whose goal is to switch souls with Ben and possess the Omnitrix. However, Charmcaster first accidentally switches identities with Gwen, and then as spells fly back and forth, Ben and Gwen even end up in one another's bodies before they team up to get rid of Charmcaster once and for all.

title: Joy Ride
description: The Cool Kids help Steven put some fun back in his life.

title: The Cat's Car
description: Tulip has to face her past.

title: Expert or Liar
description: Rigby wants to redeem himself by winning on "Expert or Liar."

title: Brain Trust
description: Dr. Fox accidentally transports the gang inside her brain, where they must control her movements to complete a dangerous experiment.

title: Infinite Vendetta Part 2
description: Starscream gives Jetfire and Skybyte Spark Armor to escalate their feud and distract everyone from his machinations.

title: Big Trouble, Little NinjaGo
description: The ninja race to save Lloyd, as a more powerful-than-ever Lord Garmadon creates an enormous Colossi to help him rule Ninjago and defeat the ninja.

title: The Mask of Deception
description: When an unknown criminal syndicate threatens the Royal Family, the Ninja are called back into action and must protect the royal princess and a fabled artifact that may hold supernatural powers.

title: Starscream's Children Part 1
description: The Autobots received a distress call from the Nemesis and must come to the aid of their arch-enemies.

title: Gathering Dark
description: Axel must help Bearbarian overcome his secret fear of the dark to stop Dynamo from stealing his ride.

title: Cat-Pocalypse
description: When Vic gets sick and is stuck in his room, he spies on Pineapple and becomes convinced that Pineapple is creating an army of zombie cats. Val agrees and the two become obsessed with stopping Pineapple before it's too late!

title: The Beach Car
description: Tulip strikes a deal with a cat in an attempt to get home, but is the price worth it?

title: The Crossroads Part 2
description: Optimus and the Autobots team up with some very familiar faces to escape Unspace.

title: I Am the Allspark Part 1
description: Starscream successfully merges with the Allspark, spelling doom for the Autobots and Decepticons.

title: The Unfinished Car
description: The gang enters an unfinished train car and tries to fix it.

title: Food Truck
description: The Bears open up a food truck after being disappointed by the food options available to them. In an effort to drum up business, they start selling their food to animals until the animals go a little crazy.

title: Secret Science Part 2
description: Wheeljack attempts to break out of the Nemesis while Windblade hunts down Bludgeon to avenge Slipstream.

title: The Great Elf Invention Convention
description: Oscar, Max, and Hedgehog do a favor for Barb the elf in exchange for some chips.

title: Earth & Water
description: Princess Bubblegum subjects Flame Princess to a series of tests to gauge Flame Princess's fiery tendencies. But when there's an emergency at the treehouse, and Princess Bubblegum leaves Cinnamon Bun to watch Flame Princess, her experiment might literally backfire in her face.

title: El Tronco es mio
description: Cuando un niño reclama posesión del Tronco, Craig no tiene otra opción que llevarlo a juicio.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Stop the Presses
description: Richard's newspapers aren't selling, so his friends pull out all the stops to put the printed word back on top.

title: Ghost Town Part 2
description: Teletraan-X attempts to rehabilitate Starscream while Optimus, Bee, Hot Rod and Cheetor's quest to save Windblade uncovers a city that is more than meets the eye.

title: Castles and Kitties
description: Score Creeper traps the gang in a fantasy role playing game where they must follow a complex set of rules to win their freedom.

title: The Comic
description: Gumball is the star of his own comic, but struggles to match up to his heroic alter-ego.

title: The Drama
description: Everyone assumes Darwin and Carrie's relationship is doomed as they're so different. That is, everyone except Darwin and Carrie. When Carrie's cool ghostly ex-boyfriend turns up, Gumball decides to get Darwin to confront what's really going on.

title: Hide and Secrets
description: Desperate for answers about Namagem, Mega Man decides to break into his father's lab, which leaves Suna exposed to the vengeful robot.

title: Exit 9B
description: Mordecai and Rigby are the only ones who can save the park after everyone gets brain washed.

title: Dread on Arrival
description: The ninja appeal to the police commissioner of Ninjago in an effort to help save Lloyd and thwart Harumi's efforts to resurrect the evil Lord Garmadon.

title: El Paseo en Autobus de Pancake
description: Manzana y Cebollín suben a un autobús que da un tour guiado como parte de su plan para recuperar el zapato de Manzana.

title: The Shortcut
description: An unusually hot day at the Creek melts all of Kit's ice pops, so Craig helps her find a short cut to her frozen snack supplier before everyone else melts.

title: Panic in the Lighthouse
description: When Chaotique breaks into Dr. Light's lab, Mega Man must shut down his frenemy and the lab's defenses before either of them gets destroyed!

title: #BurritoBucket
description: Babs loves her job at fast food restaurant Burrito Bucket, but her boss, who's fed up with her chronic lateness and bad case of scatterbrain, would love any excuse to fire her. When a bank robbery breaks out right across the street from work, Babs is torn between her role as a superhero and dutiful Burrito Bucket employee. Will she be able to save the day and keep her job all in the nick of time?

title: Dungeon Train
description: All aboard! Finn and Jake discover a train where every car is a dungeon filled with a new foe for Finn to fight. Jake quickly gets bored and wants to leave, but Finn is having the BEST time and doesn't want to leave... ever!

title: Midnight Madness
description: When the Rustbucket breaks down outside the largest mall in the U.S., it seems Ben and Gwen will have the time of their lives in the mall. That is until they run into an evil hypnotist entertaining the crowd, who puts Ben under hypnosis, causing him to sleepwalk at night and help him steal things. And when the hypnotist discovers certain aliens are now helping him, he exploits them for his grand plan of hypnotizing hundreds of people so they'll be under his demented control forever. Ben must figure out how to break the spell he's under and stop this evil plan.

title: Presidential Punchout
description: When Morbucks enters the Student Body President race, Blossom sinks to her level to secure the win.

title: Look Who's Clocking
description: When Harold's warnings not to mess with the clock go ignored, the kids are forced to save themselves when Duncan tears a hole in the fabric of time.

title: Wiped Out Part 1
description: Out in space to catch some solar waves, Bumblebee, Hot Rod and Cheetor discover the asteroid remains of a mysterious planet.

title: Exodus Part 2
description: Fleeing the destruction of their home planet Thundera, Lion-O and the ThunderCats land on the mysterious, dangerous, all-around awesome world of Third Earth! But their enemies, the Mutants of Plun-Darr have followed them and it turns out Third Earth already has a Mumm-Ra problem, can Lion-O learn the ropes of being a leader in time?

title: The Gauntlet Part 2
description: As Dr. Light and Suna turn the Robot Masters against each other, Mega Man defeats and unmasks his arch nemeses, Lord Obsidian, who turns out to be Sgt. Night in disguise, and finally learns the identity of Namagem, Mega Man's long lost twin brother!

title: Dark Birth Part 2
description: The Autobots and Decepticons battle aboard the Nemesis while Starscream uses the Allspark and Vector Sigma to create new allies.

title: Adrenaland Jr.
description: Team Tennyson visits the safety-neutered version of Adrenaland known as "Adrenaland Jr.", only to end up facing off against a bitter Kevin 11, out to destroy everyone else's good, and safe, time.

title: Uncle Fashion
description: Uncle Grandpa helps a young boy who wants to be a fashion designer by taking him somewhere his style will be appreciated.

title: Room for Ruby
description: Steven's Gem family continues to grow.

title: The Oni & the Dragon
description: While Princess Harumi adjusts to life with the ninja, Lloyd and Jay search for answers about the Oni Masks, while Cole and Zane attempt to infiltrate the Sons of Garmadon.

title: Our Brand is Chaos
description: Bubbles and Buttercup make a deal without realizing the consequences.

title: Terror llegando
description: Los ninjas recurren al comisionado de la policía de Ninjago en un esfuerzo por ayudar a salvar a Lloyd y frustrar los esfuerzos de Harumi de resucitar al malvado Lord Garmadon.

title: Midnight Quittance
description: Ramona invites Hedgehog and Oscar to participate in a special holiday ritual.

title: Uncle Grandpa Babies
description: When the President calls in the Uncle Grandpa babies, they have to act quickly and use their special baby powers to defuse a missile.

title: The Ball Pit Car
description: The gang is confronted by a strange new force on a Ball Pit Car adventure.

title: The Great Fossil Rush
description: JP finds a fossil in the Creek which quickly causes the landscape to change.

title: Spell Crushers
description: Hedgehog tries to get over a crush so she can regain her focus on magic.

title: The Chrome Car
description: The gang meets a familiar face in a mirrored car.

title: Spotted Part 2
description: Cheetor's scout training with Bee lands them in the clutches of Starscream who tests an evil experiment on them.

title: El oni y el dragon
description: Mientras que la Princesa Harumi se adapta a la vida con los ninjas, Lloyd y Jay buscan respuestas sobre las máscaras Oni, mientras que Cole y Zane intentan infiltrarse en Los Hijos de Garmadon.
